{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act37side", "eventName": "追跡日落以西", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GO-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "鏽王冠", "storyInfo": "偷竊王冠的退役士兵主動出現在維娜的面前，試圖勸說維娜成為她心中所期待的那個國王，但維娜依舊選擇將王冠空置於王座之上。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g3_westlobbythroneroom", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>我不喜歡聖王會西部大堂裡的那個王座廳。空蕩蕩，陰森森的。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>那座王座就那麼擺在那裡，冷冷清清的……我真的沒辦法想像，假如維娜真坐上去會是什麼畫面。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>一個人，獨自坐在那張冰冷的椅子上，望著那些空無一物的台階——</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>以維娜的性格，她絕對待不超過一分鐘……我敢打賭。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>聖王會西部大堂王座廳</><p=2>1098年12月23日 3:26 A.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王冠找到了？現在在哪裡？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚴格來說不能算找到，是有人把它送到了議長辦公室。至於確切的丟失時間，不太好確認，但大致能確定是在你演講開始之後。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……之前維娜就把王冠放在那座空王座上。可偷走這個東西能有什麼好處？是那些公爵指使的嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想不是。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵們從來不是一個團體，他們各有盤算。不過王冠丟失這件事偏偏和他們同時來倫蒂尼姆撞上，這也未免太巧了點。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但照你的說法，那個東西現在不就只是有點歷史的破鐵圈嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_229_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呃，摩根，並非如此。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管它現在是什麼樣子，王冠對很多人來說象徵著維多利亞的榮耀。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它被擱置了二十多年，許多人非但沒有忘記它，反而更加期待——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……期待有朝一日，會有一位賢明的君主戴上它，期待新的國王能一掃維多利亞的陰霾。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，更多人只是迫切地想要一個“奇蹟”來滿足他們對王權的渴望與崇拜。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，這點我無法否認。而且這樣的聲音，你應該不陌生。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的身分本來就與眾不同。你是王室後裔，是無可爭議的戰爭英雄，卻又在街頭長大，這讓很多人自然對你產生了認同感。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再加上議會順利成立，公爵們的主動讓權，他們更會深信你已經得到了所有人的支持。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來的事，無非就是水到渠成——", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是那些公爵真正的想法根本不是這樣！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_229_1#5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，民眾只會在乎結果。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#5"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊……從我們回到這裡的那天起，我就清楚這一點了。可惜我有時候還是很擅長讓人失望。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g6_dusklentiavenue", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>新奧克特里格區街道</><p=2>1098年12月23日 4:59 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生，謝謝您分享的能量棒！如果每次都有這麼美味的謝禮，我還真樂意天天來接受你的身體檢查，哈哈！", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在哥倫比亞，這些真的都是商品嗎？你們哥倫比亞人為什麼會習慣囤積這些東西？也是為了應對天災嗎？", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有啦，這只是我的個人習慣。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直覺得吃飯無非就是補充能量和營養的過程，既然能量棒能讓這個過程更高效，那為什麼要拒絕呢？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，不過黛安總是說我這種想法很不可取就是了。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也不奇怪，畢竟在現在的倫蒂尼姆，能填飽肚子就該感謝了。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這已經是亞歷山德莉娜殿下付出巨大努力的結果了。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹嘛和他說這些……", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生，謝謝您帶來這些……呃，“能量棒”。但您該走了。", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯坦利，你該不會害怕埃利西奧先生會——", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有！", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我總不能當著別人的面，為這種蠢事跟你吵起來吧？", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，他不喜歡我尊稱亞歷山德莉娜為“殿下”，就這麼簡單。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟斯坦利在政見上一直不太合。我覺得有個國王也不是壞事，但他呢，堅持認為當初有國王的時候我們過得更慘。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但您看，無論從前還是現在，我們的日子不還是一樣照過？", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以您是說，有沒有國王，對你們的生活根本沒影響？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管她怎麼想，事實就是，就算王座上還有人坐，也輪不到我們去吃加冕宴。", "name": "侷促的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_417_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，斯坦利，你什麼時候才能拿出更有說服力的理由啊？", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生，抱歉，我又得花點時間開導這個死腦筋了。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，關於城裡城防軍頻繁出動的原因，我確實聽說了一點流言——好像是有人偷走了王冠，巡邏隊正在調查相關的人。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，斯坦利。再見，埃利西奧先生。", "name": "悠閒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不過，黛安倒是從來沒提過關於國王或王冠的事。或許回去後該問問她的看法。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "43_g7_towngreenhouse", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃利西奧先生，您應該休息一下，您幾乎一直在外面協助收集病例資料。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡的感染者幾乎都是在同一時期急性發病，而且結果異常少見。我必須盡可能記錄下這些珍貴的資料。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是未來用於礦石病的研究，還是為倫蒂尼姆市民開發專門的藥物，這些資料都非常重要。", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，莎拉女士，黛安今天怎麼沒有來探望你？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安？", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為她在幫忙你呢。今天有不少老戰友來療養院想問問最近有沒有什麼異常情況，原本還想拉著黛安一起聚聚的。", "name": "療養院患者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？", "name": "埃利西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_487_bobb_1#11$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g8_siegeoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>直到戰爭結束，維娜也從沒告訴我們，她到底在哪裡找到那頂王冠。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>但這不重要，沒人在乎，也不會再有人見到那個鐵圈了。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>它將被永遠封存在聖王會西部大堂的王座廳內，直到徹底侵蝕、腐朽殆盡。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>“國王的時代已經結束了。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>這是維娜喝醉後，摟著我的脖子說的話。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>然而，才不過兩個多月，它就這麼光明正大地出現在我們眼前——這座古老帝國的幽靈，從未停止糾纏它的下一個受害者。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>議長辦公室</><p=2>1098年12月24日 6:26 A.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有其他人知道這件事嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經在封鎖消息了，我們會盡可能把影響降到最低。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那這個東西該怎麼處理？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根指著辦公桌上的王冠，它已滿是傷痕。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是第一次這麼近距離看到……這麼多人在乎的東西……就是這個？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜……維娜？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她發現維娜根本沒有把目光放在王冠上，而是沉默地倚靠在辦公桌前，注視著眼前那個垂頭喪氣的人——"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“竊取王冠的人”。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，你真的什麼都不打算問我嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我大概能猜到。你們很多人對我抱有……不切實際的幻想。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，關於這件事，我的同僚們很快就會整理出完整客觀的報告送到我桌上。所以——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把我跟那些人混為一談！他們在乎的是那張王座，而我在乎的是坐在王座上的人。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜議長，我很清楚自己在做什麼，議會頒布的每一條新法我都記得一清二楚。私闖王座廳確實是重罪，我不打算狡辯。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這不代表你和他們本質上有什麼不同。你的罪行，臨時法庭會依據法律來審理。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是否還有其他異議？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，閣下。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩，剩下的事就交給你了。王冠我會親自送回王座廳，之後也會加強戒備。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，然後我還得去議會準備向議員們彙報的稿子……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵……彙報。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王，你根本不需要做這些。你很清楚議會的低效率——它只不過是讓某些人能夠平衡自身利益的地方罷了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光是應付那些議員就已經夠讓你疲憊了，不是嗎？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的倫蒂尼姆最需要的不是一個受議會監管的議長，而是一位能夠帶領整座城市變革的領袖。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，沒必要跟她爭論這些沒意義的事。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4110_delphn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，戴菲恩。女士，你的意思是，倫蒂尼姆需要一位獨裁者？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我指的是國王。維多利亞的國王。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我大概能猜到你的計劃，閣下……你跟我認識的每一任掌權者都不一樣。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你甚至完全不在乎自己的血統。但如果想要實現你的想法，“議長”這個身分……遠遠不夠。這頂王冠，既不該，也不會成為你的阻礙。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她站起身，筆直地向維娜敬了一個軍禮。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是所有我想說的了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "典範軍，推進之王，謝謝你們為這片家園所做的一切。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#7$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很喜歡她的改變，也堅信她的未來將比過去更加美好。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只可惜這場變革還是太慢了……我恐怕沒辦法等到那一天了。", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩閣下，走吧，接下來我要去哪？", "name": "黛安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1519_1#2$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你……真的知道我想要做什麼嗎？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“你想要改變維多利亞……”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“不，你想要打敗它，打敗過去的維多利亞。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "55_g3_westlobbythroneroom", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜站在階梯之下，手中捧著王冠，注視著王座。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王座一旁，金色的獅子趴在地上，眼皮半垂著。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，你應該直接告訴我的。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一步步踏上階梯，走到王座前卻沒有坐上去，而是坐在了台階上。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師似乎沒有睜開眼，他的鼻息輕輕拂過鬃毛，也揚起了些許塵埃。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有些不滿。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，老師，我又熬了一夜。還有很多棘手的事還沒解決……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她感受到背後傳來的溫暖——金色的獅子靠近了些，那龐大的身軀成了她的依靠……"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像小時候那樣，維娜聞到了陽光的味道。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，如果能就這樣靠在你身邊睡著該有多好。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從城外一路走回來，就像做了一場夢……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我明明已經很久沒能痛痛快快地睡上一覺，做一場好夢了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獅子微微抬起頭，蹭了蹭維娜的金色頭髮，讓她覺得有點癢。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寒冷的空氣讓維娜輕輕打了個顫，稍微清醒了一些。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這裡……一直這麼冷嗎？還不到休息的時候啊。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在能做的還遠遠不夠。不夠發的藥品、不夠分的糧食，還有永遠吵不完的架——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候我真的恨不得脫下這身衣服，把那些混蛋一個個揍趴下。說不定這樣事情就簡單多了，不是嗎？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“打敗那個過去的維多利亞”……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是這真的只是一場擂台賽，那該有多好啊。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金色的獅子閉上眼，睡著了，但尾巴還是不自覺地拍打著維娜的手臂。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，抱歉，又再跟你抱怨了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些話我不知道該怎麼跟摩根她們說。她們可能無法理解，而我也不想讓她們擔心。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩……在她面前，我也不想表現得太過迷惘。她已經替我分擔了太多，對我也寄予了太多期待。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……老師，現在已經有更多的人倚靠著我了。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想辜負他們。", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她閉上眼，緊緊握住王冠。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“國王”、“議長”，這些頭銜對她來說，一點意義都沒有。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只是想——"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "維娜，你果然在這！"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "摩根", "content": "欸……你剛剛睡著了……"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是在想一些事。老師他——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她下意識側過頭，卻什麼也沒有看到。但那份溫暖，依舊清晰。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他走了。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……老師，謝謝你陪著我。）", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，你怎麼找到這裡來了？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩已經說服臨時法庭，暫時把那個偷走王冠的人安置在城防軍營地的禁閉房裡。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於她的完整報告也已經整理好了，我不想耽誤就立刻帶來給你。這份就是報告。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她叫黛安·韋伯。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根停頓了一下，似乎在等著維娜的反應。但維娜只是好奇地看著她，等她繼續說下去。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是臨時起意偷走王冠的。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這之前的很長一段時間，她一直跟著一名來自哥倫比亞的醫藥代表，幫忙向城裡的人普及礦石病感染後的自我防護知識。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就是這樣摸清了聖王會西部大堂外巡邏隊的換班時間，最後趁著你廣播演講時溜進了王座廳。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後她在裡面待了很久，至少半個小時。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她做了什麼？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道。她不肯說，也許是猶豫不決，也許只是發呆。但最後她還是順利帶著王冠離開，沒有驚動任何人——", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，這不對。她在王座廳待了這麼久，離開的時候沒有碰上換班後的巡邏隊？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，她離開的時候順利到她自己都覺得驚訝，她也以為自己一定會被巡邏隊逮住。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以一定有人幫了她。是那幾位“客人”？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不確定。但她自己完全不知情，她是自發這麼做的，沒有任何同夥。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……為什麼？就只是為了把王冠帶到我面前，想要說服我——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是黛安·韋伯。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道——", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你不記得她了。我一直覺得她很眼熟，直到看到報告才終於確定她果然是——", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得那天我們被聯軍包圍在家門口時，第一個違抗命令、護送我們繼續前進的士兵嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜回想起那天的天空，籠罩著整座城市的蒸汽與未散的硝煙。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那名在記憶中已經變得模糊的士兵。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“聯軍第六縱隊第十步兵團中尉黛安·韋伯命令小隊全體放下武器，護送典範軍繼續前進！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我是一名士兵，但更是出生在這裡的倫蒂尼姆人……這裡也是我的家。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“推進之王，撐住，我們還得繼續並肩作戰。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“為了奪回屬於我們的一切！”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛安·韋伯，那名違抗開斯特公爵命令的士兵……她在與食腐者之王的最後一戰裡，最終還是沒能躲過急性感染。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得嗎？她就是那個從你手中接過“諸王之息”然後衝向食腐者的士兵。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "維娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她撐不了多久了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為城裡礦石病抑制劑短缺，她一直沒有分到足夠的藥來延緩病情發展。我們幫她做了檢查，但是……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王冠在維娜逐漸握緊的手中發出輕微的金屬摩擦聲。它看起來如此脆弱，卻又異常堅韌。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的確熱愛這片家園，也熱愛維多利亞。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以她選擇加入公爵的部隊，又違背命令，最終被迫退役。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她很信任你，雖然我完全不認同她的一些想法。但是，維娜，我們或許可以……", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>我到最後也沒有把為黛安求情的話說出口。維娜很清楚我想說什麼，而我也清楚維娜會怎麼回答……</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>不，應該說，我知道維娜·維多利亞議長會怎麼回答。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>直到今天我仍無法想像黛安·韋伯當時是懷抱著怎樣的心情才會做出那樣荒唐的決定。但我由衷地敬佩她。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>……一名偷走王冠，卻又真心愛著維多利亞的人。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>我不明白，自從回到這座城市後很多事都變了，變得讓我無法理解，也不願理解……</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>也正是在那一天，我終於下定決心——</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "<i>從聖王會西部大堂前的最後一戰結束至今，我已經在這裡待得太久了……</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n<i>或許是時候回家了，回到我的拳館。</i>", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}